==Useful Info==
The '''Iron Giant''' is a [[unique]] [[stone giant]] found only in [[Dungeon Sprint]]. Instead of throwing [[large rock]]s, he will shoot you with powerful [[Iron Shot]]s and will summon [[iron elemental]]s to support him. On top of that, he has [[resistance]]s to most elements, immunity to [[Silence]], and hits like a truck in melee. Have fun!

<!--spl-bot-begin-->
